                              <height>210-213</height>
                              <width>162-165</width>
                           </dimensions>). Blað <locus from="22v" to="22v">22v</locus> er autt og neðri
                        hluti blaðs <locus from="22r" to="22r">22r</locus>.</extent>
                        <foliation>
